<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als uns <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>gut<ex>en</ex></expan> frewnde der von Basel und ewr
              <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add>auf <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> schrift</add> nehst von
                <expan>Nördling<ex>en</ex></expan> herab <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als ir das von <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> nu wol <expan>vernome<ex>n</ex></expan> habt, also
                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> seid bey uns aufgehalten in gut, daz wir
                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etwas meͣr <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan>; so haben wir seid der zeit niht
              <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>treffenlich<ex>er</ex></expan> meͣr <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>.
                <expan>W<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>, ob wir hinfür icht <expan>treffenlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
            mer <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan>, die uns <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>notdurft<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>wurde<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>dunke<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>zu v<ex>er</ex>künden</expan>, das <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
              <add>ewch</add>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add>zu wissen</add> tun, <expan>desgleich<ex>en</ex></expan> wir uns zu ewch auch
                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sehen</expan>. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
